locality: OINNE RIVER VALLEY: Oinné River valley, on road towards Mt. Dzumac, from Dumbéa valley. Forested slopes.
Haute Rivière des Pirogues: Forêt Faux Bon Secours.
Bwa Bwi, contrefort sud-est, cuvette sous le camp.

Upper Tchamba River valley. Along logging road S of Wâo Uni, just N of point 616 m. Forest along road. Non-ultramafic substrate. Collected with J. Munzinger, M. Schlessman, L. Vary, A. Mouly & T. Le Borgne.
